What is Product Management?

Product Management in Odoo is the process of creating, organizing, and maintaining all the products and services that a company buys or sells.

It helps businesses:

Maintain product information
Set selling prices
Track inventory (for storable products)
Apply taxes
Categorize products
Manage product variants
Real World Example

ABC Technologies sells:

Computer
Laptop
Printer
Monitor
Keyboard
Mouse
Odoo ERP Implementation (Service)

All these items are managed through the Products module.

